### Get all animals
GET http://localhost:8080/api/animals
Accept: application/json

---

### Get a single animal by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/animals/{animalId}
Accept: application/json

---

### Create a new animal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/animals/specie/{specieId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 5,
  "weight": 300.5
}

---

### Update an existing animal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/animals/{animalId}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 6,
  "weight": 320.0
}

---

### Delete an animal by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/animals/{animalId}
